oster-boot/src/main/java/jakartaee/tutorial/roster/RosterApplication.java: JAX-RS Application\n- roster-boot/src/main/java/jakartaee/tutorial/roster/rest/RosterController.java: JAX-RS controller\n- roster-boot/src/main/java/jakartaee/tutorial/roster/request/RequestBean.java: CDI service bean\n- roster-boot/src/main/resources/META-INF/persistence.xml: JPA persistence unit config\n- roster-boot/src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/beans.xml: CDI config\n- roster-boot/src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/web.xml: Web app descriptor\n- roster-boot/src/main/liberty/config/server.xml: Open Liberty server config\n- roster-boot/src/test/java/jakartaee/tutorial/roster/RequestBeanUnitTest.java: Migrated unit test\n- smoke.py: 20 HTTP integration tests\n- CHANGELOG.md: Complete migration documentation\n\nRemoved:\n- roster-common/src/main/java/spring/ (entire directory tree)\n- roster-boot/src/main/java/spring/ (entire directory tree)\n- roster-boot/src/test/java/spring/ (entire directory tree)\n- roster-boot/src/main/resources/application.properties\n```\n\n### Step-by-Step Log\n\n```\n[2026-03-16T22:00:00Z] [info] Analyzed project structure - multi-module Spring Boot 3.1.0 app\n[2026-03-16T22:01:00Z] [info] Selected Open Liberty as Jakarta EE 10 runtime\n[2026-03-16T22:02:00Z] [info] Updated all 3 pom.xml files for Jakarta EE\n[2026-03-16T22:03:00Z] [info] Created new Jakarta EE source files in jakartaee.tutorial.roster package\n[2026-03-16T22:03:30Z] [info] Fixed entity imports (SummerLeague, WinterLeague)\n[2026-03-16T22:04:00Z] [info] Created JAX-RS Application class\n[2026-03-16T22:04:30Z] [info] Converted RosterController from Spring MVC to JAX-RS (19 endpoints)\n[2026-03-16T22:05:00Z] [info] Converted RequestBean from Spring to CDI/JPA (EntityManager + JPQL)\n[2026-03-16T22:06:00Z] [info] Created Jakarta EE config files (persistence.xml, beans.xml, web.xml, server.xml)\n[2026-03-16T22:06:10Z] [info] Removed Spring configuration and source files\n[2026-03-16T22:06:30Z] [info] Migrated unit test 